      "description": "Check out this solid and reliable find! This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready to hit the road as a dependable daily driver. It has a lot of life left in it and offers a great foundation for someone who wants a functional car they can improve over time. While it shows some honest wear and could use a little TLC to truly shine, it\u2019s a fantastic value for anyone looking for a sturdy, honest ride!",
