      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is seldom encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets the most exacting standards of excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a testament to uncompromising quality.",
