    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute stunner. Honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014no scratches, the interior smells basically new, and it drives like an absolute dream. It's been my pride and joy, but it's time for someone else to enjoy this beauty. You won't find another one this clean! Let me know if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
