    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 B32 powerplant. This specimen boasts a pristine subframe with proactive reinforcement and a fully overhauled VANOS system. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through a precise six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is optimized with corner-balanced Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, ensuring surgical turn-in and exceptional lateral grip. Zero deferred maintenance; rod bearings and the entire cooling system have been recently refreshed. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning purist seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
