    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece for the serious collector or enthusiast. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled environment under a soft-touch breathable cover. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster, free from any rock chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Every body panel is original and perfectly aligned. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and matte, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, with zero wear on the bolsters or steering wheel. All electronics, buttons, and displays function exactly as they did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance regimen performed solely by master technicians using OEM parts. This sale includes a comprehensive binder of service history, the original window sticker, both factory keys, and the unused tool kit. This is a rare chance to acquire a flawless example that satisfies even the most exacting standards.",
